WEBVTT

00:11.840 --> 00:12.960
CHAPTER VII—GRATITUDE

00:12.960 --> 00:17.680
The illustrations given in the last chapter will have conveyed to the reader the fact

00:17.680 --> 00:22.560
that the first step toward getting rich is to convey the idea of your wants to the formless

00:22.560 --> 00:23.180
substance.

00:23.900 --> 00:29.440
This is true, and you will see that in order to do so, it becomes necessary to relate yourself

00:29.440 --> 00:32.060
to the formless intelligence in a harmonious way.

00:32.800 --> 00:37.820
To secure this harmonious relation is a matter of such primary and vital importance that

00:37.820 --> 00:42.640
I shall give some space to its discussion here, and give you instructions which, if

00:42.640 --> 00:47.160
you will follow them, will be certain to bring you into perfect unity of mind with God.

00:47.640 --> 00:53.120
The whole process of mental adjustment and atonement can be summed up in one word—gratitude.

00:53.760 --> 00:58.320
First, you believe that there is one intelligent substance, from which all things proceed.

00:58.320 --> 01:02.520
Second, you believe that this substance gives you everything you desire.

01:02.840 --> 01:07.780
And third, you relate yourself to it by a feeling of deep and profound gratitude.

01:08.560 --> 01:13.900
Many people who order their lives rightly in all other ways are kept in poverty by their

01:13.900 --> 01:14.980
lack of gratitude.

01:15.600 --> 01:21.240
Having received one gift from God, they cut the wires which connect them with Him by failing

01:21.240 --> 01:22.380
to make acknowledgement.

01:22.820 --> 01:27.980
It is easy to understand that the nearer we live to the source of wealth, the more wealth

01:27.980 --> 01:28.940
we shall receive.

01:29.260 --> 01:34.140
And it is easy also to understand that the soul that is always grateful lives in closer

01:34.140 --> 01:38.420
touch with God than the one which never looks to Him in thankful acknowledgement.

01:39.100 --> 01:44.000
The more gratefully we fix our minds on the Supreme when good things come to us, the more

01:44.000 --> 01:47.620
good things we will receive, and the more rapidly they will come.

01:47.880 --> 01:52.980
And the reason simply is that the mental attitude of gratitude draws the mind into closer touch

01:52.980 --> 01:55.120
with the source from which the blessings come.

01:55.820 --> 02:00.780
If it is a new thought to you, that gratitude brings your whole mind into closer harmony

02:00.780 --> 02:05.380
with the creative energies of the universe, consider it well, and you will see that it

02:05.380 --> 02:05.940
is true.

02:06.420 --> 02:11.320
The good things you already have, have come to you along the line of obedience to certain

02:11.320 --> 02:11.760
laws.

02:12.420 --> 02:17.320
Gratitude will lead your mind out along the ways by which things come, and it will keep

02:17.320 --> 02:21.940
you in close harmony with creative thought and prevent you from falling into competitive

02:21.940 --> 02:22.400
thought.

02:23.580 --> 02:27.940
Gratitude alone can keep you looking toward the All, and prevent you from falling into

02:27.940 --> 02:33.060
the error of thinking of the supply as limited, and to do that would be fatal to your hopes.

02:33.800 --> 02:38.520
There is a law of gratitude, and it is absolutely necessary that you should observe the law,

02:38.900 --> 02:40.860
if you are to get the results you seek.

02:41.540 --> 02:46.300
The law of gratitude is the natural principle that action and reaction are always equal

02:46.300 --> 02:47.900
and in opposite directions.

02:48.440 --> 02:54.200
The grateful outreaching of your mind in thankful praise to the Supreme is a liberation or expenditure

02:54.200 --> 02:54.840
of force.

02:55.380 --> 03:00.640
It cannot fail to reach that to which it addressed, and the reaction is an instantaneous movement

03:00.640 --> 03:01.560
towards you.

03:02.100 --> 03:05.680
Draw nigh unto God, and He will draw nigh unto you.

03:06.120 --> 03:08.700
That is a statement of psychological truth.

03:09.420 --> 03:14.460
And if your gratitude is strong and constant, the reaction in formless substance will be

03:14.460 --> 03:15.660
strong and continuous.

03:16.180 --> 03:19.440
The movement of the things you want will be always toward you.

03:19.940 --> 03:24.320
Notice the grateful attitude that Jesus took, how He always seems to be saying,

03:24.620 --> 03:27.680
I thank Thee, Father, that Thou hearest me.

03:28.300 --> 03:33.260
You cannot exercise much power without gratitude, for it is gratitude that keeps you connected

03:33.260 --> 03:34.040
with power.

03:34.800 --> 03:39.040
But the value of gratitude does not consist solely in getting you more blessings in the

03:39.040 --> 03:39.460
future.

03:39.460 --> 03:44.640
Without gratitude, you cannot long keep from dissatisfied thoughts regarding things as

03:44.640 --> 03:45.280
they are.

03:45.660 --> 03:50.320
The moment you permit your mind to dwell with dissatisfaction upon things as they are, you

03:50.320 --> 03:51.480
begin to lose ground.

03:52.040 --> 03:57.860
You fix attention upon the common, the ordinary, the poor, and the squalid and mean, and your

03:57.860 --> 04:00.080
mind takes the form of these things.

04:00.580 --> 04:05.860
Then you will transmit these forms or mental images to the formless, and the common, the

04:05.860 --> 04:08.340
poor, the squalid, the mean will come to you.

04:08.340 --> 04:13.560
To permit your mind to dwell upon the inferior is to become inferior and to surround yourself

04:13.560 --> 04:14.780
with inferior things.

04:15.360 --> 04:19.720
On the other hand, to fix your attention on the best is to surround yourself with the

04:19.720 --> 04:21.400
best and to become the best.

04:21.960 --> 04:26.860
The creative power within us makes us into the image of that to which we give our attention.

04:27.480 --> 04:32.400
We are thinking substance, and thinking substance always takes the form of that to which it

04:32.400 --> 04:33.120
thinks about.

04:33.460 --> 04:36.720
The grateful mind is constantly fixed upon the best.

04:37.120 --> 04:39.120
Therefore, it tends to become the best.

04:39.380 --> 04:43.160
It takes the form or character of the best, and will receive the best.

04:43.880 --> 04:46.300
Also, faith is born of gratitude.

04:46.720 --> 04:52.020
The grateful mind continually expects good things, and expectation becomes faith.

04:52.440 --> 04:57.640
The reaction of gratitude upon one's own mind produces faith, and every outgoing wave

04:57.640 --> 05:00.060
of grateful thanksgiving increases faith.

05:00.060 --> 05:05.240
He who has no feeling of gratitude cannot long retain a living faith, and without a

05:05.240 --> 05:10.620
living faith you cannot get rich by the creative method, as we shall see in the following chapters.

05:11.480 --> 05:16.100
It is necessary, then, to cultivate the habit of being grateful for every good thing that

05:16.100 --> 05:18.720
comes to you, and to give thanks continuously.

05:19.560 --> 05:24.200
And because all things have contributed to your advancement, you should include all things

05:24.200 --> 05:25.120
in your gratitude.

05:25.820 --> 05:31.140
Do not waste time thinking or talking about the shortcomings or wrong actions of plutocrats

05:31.140 --> 05:32.140
or trust magnets.

05:32.880 --> 05:35.780
Their organization of the world has made your opportunity.

05:36.440 --> 05:38.800
All you get really comes to you because of them.

05:39.400 --> 05:41.620
Do not rage against corrupt politicians.

05:42.200 --> 05:47.060
If it were not for politicians we should fall into anarchy, and your opportunity would be

05:47.060 --> 05:47.980
greatly lessened.

05:48.380 --> 05:53.080
God has worked a long time and very patiently to bring us up to where we are in industry

05:53.080 --> 05:55.980
and government, and He is going right on with His work.

05:56.640 --> 06:02.080
There is not the least doubt that He will do away the plutocrats, trust magnets, captains

06:02.080 --> 06:05.660
of industry, and politicians as soon as they can be spared.

06:05.920 --> 06:08.940
But in the meantime, behold, they are all very good.

06:09.460 --> 06:13.920
Remember that they are all helping to arrange the lines of transmission along which your

06:13.920 --> 06:17.020
riches will come to you, and be grateful to them all.

06:17.460 --> 06:22.000
This will bring you into harmonious relations with the good in everything, and the good

06:22.000 --> 06:24.040
in everything will move toward you.

